1. download vim insteller for win or zip from offical site or github homepage
2. install or unpackage it in your partical folder, including vim and gvim
3. set the installing path as one of your system surrounding variable which named path in your system
4. now, we can input conmande vim in our windows' console to run vim
5. by the way, we also can edit our own profile for vim in User's home folder or $VIM/_vimrc
6. vim's font size will be consistant with the console's
